# ChangeLog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
Todas as mudanças notáveis neste projeto serão documentadas neste arquivo.


## [ 2.1 ] - 2021-04-09 ##################################################

### Added / Adicionado
	- Verification of input of arguments in build and install.
###

### Changed / Modificado
	- Script optimization and elimination of subshell creation.
###

### Fixed / Corrigido
	- Error treatment of updating of the data base.
	- Verification of existing and installed packages.
###

##########################################################################


## [ 2.0 ] - 2021-03-28 ##################################################

